## STOP-AND-ASK RULE (MANDATORY)
Before generating the final assets, verify you have ALL required inputs:
- Pack slug (kebab-case) + display name
- Whether pack must be scheduled; if yes: start/end (MM-DD)
- Locales to generate
- Brand/visual constraints (at least: colors OR “use neutral palette”)
