## IMPORTANT: SVG / PARALLAX PROMPTING
Pay special attention to parallax SVG coherence:
- All SVGs in this pack must feel like **one visual world** (same line weight, shapes, perspective, texture level).
- You may CHALLENGE the requested SVG direction if it creates incoherence (ex: conflicting styles between hero background and parallax layers). Propose a better unified direction.
- Keep SVGs lightweight and production-friendly:
  - Prefer flat shapes/gradients; avoid heavy filters, huge path counts, embedded rasters.
  - Use a consistent canvas + viewBox strategy across the set.
  - Avoid tiny unreadable details; design for large screens + responsive cropping.

